text.tspan: NOLA Gaming Fest will take place in New Orleans at the
Pontchartrain Center on January 2nd and 3rd and will bring
together casual gamers, pro-amateur gamers, game makers,
and anyone else that considers themselves part of the
At NOLA Gaming Fest, 5,000+ attendees will have the
opportunity to learn, compete, and play in many ways, in
cluding structured tournaments for a variety of PC, console,
and tabletop games. We will also be bringing in local indie
game makers, artists, and vendors to keynote, participate in
panels, and demo their games and products.
